Using a JSON template,

1) Create file in templates folder.

"templates/collection.json" code
{
  "sections": {
    "main": {
      "type": "main-collection-product-grid"
    }
  },
  "order": ["main"]
}

This tells Shopify to use the main-collection-product-grid section for the /collections/* pages.

2) Create "sections/main-collection-product-grid.liquid".

NOte : check code on 4.1

